=== 由肟制取 ===

也可由[[肟|肟]]与[[格氏试剂|格氏试剂]]反应制备某些氮丙环，称为“[[Hoch-Campbell氮丙环合成|Hoch-Campbell氮丙环合成]]”：<ref>Hoch, Compt. rend., 196, 1865 ('''1934'''); (a), ibid., aOS, 799 (1936); (e), ibid., 204, 358 (1937).</ref><ref>''The action of Grignard reagents on oximes. i. The action of phenylmagnesium bromide on mixed ketoximes'' Kenneth N. Campbell, James F. Mckenna [[J._Org._Chem.|J. Org. Chem.]]; '''1939'''; 4(2); 198-205. {{DOI|10.1021/jo01214a012}}</ref><ref>''The reaction of Grignard reagents with oximes. ii. The action of aryl grignard reagents with mixed ketoximes'' Kenneth N. Campbell, Barbara Knapp Campbell, Elmer Paul Chaput [[J._Org._Chem.|J. Org. Chem.]]; '''1943'''; 8(1); 99-102. {{DOI|10.1021/jo01189a015}}</ref><ref>''The action of Grignard reagents on oximes. iii. The mechanism of the action of arylmagnesium halides on mixed ketoximes. A new synthesis of ethyleneimines'' Kenneth N. Campbell, Barbara K. Campbell, James F. Mckenna, and Elmer Paul Chaput [[J._Org._Chem.|J. Org. Chem.]]; '''1943'''; pp 103 - 109; {{DOI|10.1021/jo01189a016}}</ref>

